2004/02/20 01:18 (-0500) muppetman

	* Glib.pm, README, NEWS: unstable release 1.036

2004/02/19 12:50 (+0100) kaffeetisch

	* Glib.xs (gperl_alloc_temp): Return NULL and complain loudly if
